messages.content: ok who was the director of the cia from 1976-81?

response: The Director of the CIA from 1976 to 1981 was **Stansfield Turner**. He served as Director of Central Intelligence from March 9, 1977, to January 20, 1981, under President Jimmy Carter. Before Turner, George H. W. Bush served as Director from January 30, 1976, to January 20, 1977.
